# Cloudflare Pages rewrites (200 = silent rewrite, 301 = redirect).
#
# Dynamic detail routes are served by a single pre-built shell page; the
# React island reads the URL and hydrates from R2 / the search API.
#
# Order matters — first match wins. Literal section roots must come before
# their splat siblings, otherwise the splat swallows the listing page.

/jobs/          /jobs/        200
/jobs/*         /job/         200

/categories/    /categories/  200
/categories/*   /categories/  200
